===========================
   Game Design
===========================

Style:
- 3rd/1st Person Shooter/Slasher

Movement:
- Jump
- Roll + Sprint

Attack types
- Melee / Ranged
- Guns
- Spells. Instant + Casting
- Environment
- Turrents / Towers
- Ally NPCs

Battles
- Many enemies
- Spawn in waves
- Defend checkpoint
- Buy upgrades
- Change terrain?
- Hire more NPCs and upgrade them.


